author: DJI
description:
🚿When operating near rivers, spray zones, or industrial sites, it’s not the drizzle you worry about—it’s the high‑pressure hits. In this stress test, the DJI Zenmuse L3 withstands direct water blasts from every angle and still delivers rock-solid LiDAR performance.


The result? Reliable and consistent data capture, even when most gear taps out. #dji #djienterprise #zenmusel3 #lidar #infrastructureinspection
title: Water vs. LiDAR: Extreme Resistance Test | Zenmuse L3
